From a support issue: "Search for 'abc' finds the pages correctly. Search for abc999 also brings back the same pages even though there is no referece to abc999 on the page."

Is this related to the way we tokenise pages for Lucene? If so, maybe we need multiple tokenisations per page, one with truncation and one without?

